Simple Java Program to Control Hue Lights

- send API Put Request Asynchronously to turn on or off multiple lights

Basic Commands: Turn on, Turn off, Set Color, Set Brightness

Other Commands:
 - Blink, Strobe: loop + Turn on + Turn off
 - Color transformation: Set color multiple times
 - Color loop: Loop color transformation
 - Dim, Brighten, Fade In, Fade Out: Set brightness + Turn on + Turn off